*Odgovoriti* mu je bio da ne može pomoći. (He answered him that he cannot help.)

Odgovorila je da ne zna. (She answered that she doesn't know.)

Nisam mogao *odgovoriti* na pitanje. (I couldn't answer the question.)

Ona je odgovorila da je u redu. (She answered that it's okay.)

On je na to *odgovorio* da je nezadovoljan. (He answered that he was dissatisfied.)